title: FSX - VoxATC 6.46 WITH CRACK
description: VoxATC is a huge advance in Flight Simulation that adds a whole new dimension to the experience. VoxATC is the first ATC add-on for FSX & Prepar3D that has been developed with integrated voice recognition. Talk to the controllers using standard ATC phraseology and what you say will be heard. Just like in the real world, requests must be properly constructed, instructions complied with and read back correctly. Some FS add-ons let you talk to the computer, with VoxATC you talk to Air Traffic Control.
